data.description: Peaceful 3 bedrooms, 2-bathroom home, perfect place for entertaining and relaxing! This house has an insulated 20x40 shop that has a half bath plumbed for shower if wanted, and kitchen, a 11x19 shipping container with slab floor, wood burning stove and electric, an additional 17x12 portable building with loft and vaulted ceilings. Hardie plank siding, large master with a study attached. RV or boat parking. New appliance in Dec. 2022, well pump replaced in 2022 to keep a Luch yard that won't raise the water bill. New HVAC in 2020 with 10 year warranty. Owners have done so many new updates you will just need to see. No need to bring your pen, your agent or I will provide 1 for you. Every inch of this property has been perfectly maintained and manicured.
